title: Osho song_Teri Aakh Ki Jadu_The magic spell .. .m4v
description:
devoted bhajan to Osho
composed by swami Gopal Bharati


translated: by Varun Duggal

The magic spell of your eyes is such
everyone gets lost in them
That a bond of several births intimate in just first sight
when u come in front us with joining hands
and give us smile
with your innocent gestures
u shower compassion nectar on us
your persona is such a magic
that it sow the seeds of love in us.

That a bond of several births intimate in just first sight
each and every valuable word of yours
is Bible,Quran and Geeta in themselves
U own tavern of awareness
one who understand drinks that wine
one who is immersed get himself vanished

whenever your love beckons
we just encircle like moths around flame
We like Meera,Buddha and Krishna 
perform musical romatic Opera with you 
your medidations are so
divine,enchanting,spellbinding,bewitchingcharming,heavenly,divine,lovely delightful)
everyone becomes like you only
